{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">1.掌握氯离子的检验方法；</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2.掌握蒸馏的原理基本操作。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">利用混合物中各组分沸点不同，用蒸馏的方法除去不挥发的杂质。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">CaCl<sub style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;2AgN<span style=\"color:#000000\">O</span><sub style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub>&nbsp;= Ca<span style=\"color:#000000\">(</span>N<span style=\"color:#000000\">O</span><sub style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">)</span><sub style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+ 2AgCl&darr;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">MgCl<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;2AgN<span style=\"color:#000000\">O</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub>&nbsp;= Mg<span style=\"color:#000000\">(</span>N<span style=\"color:#000000\">O</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">)</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+ 2AgCl&darr;</span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：蒸馏烧瓶、铁架台、铁夹、火柴、酒精灯、温度计、药匙、石棉网、冷凝管、锥形瓶、尾接管、橡胶管、胶头滴管、试管。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：沸石、自来水、硝酸银溶液、稀硝酸。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">1.在试管中加入少量自来水，滴入几滴稀硝酸使溶液酸化，然后再加几滴硝酸银溶液，观察实验现象；</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2.在蒸馏烧瓶中加入约1/3体积的自来水，用药匙加入几粒沸石，插好温度计，并使温度计的水银球位于支管口处。连通水管，通入冷凝水，然后加热烧瓶，弃去刚开始馏出的部分液体，用锥形瓶收集约10ml液体，停止加热；<br />\n3.取少量收集到的液体加入试管中，然后滴加几滴稀硝酸和硝酸银溶液，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">1.有白色沉淀产生；</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2.无明显现象。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}